{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Escape Everlit</i> is a narrative-oriented point-n-click adventure game, created by the one-person <i>Lantao Studio</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968970/extras/Timeline_3_eng_scaled_hq.gif?t=1729223069\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- <strong>Enigmatic yet Realistic Sci-Fi Mystery</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Set in near-future China, four protagonists with vastly different ages, professions, personalities, and mindsets find themselves mysteriously transported from the heart of a city to a strange villa on a remote island among endless ocean. To return to their normal lives, they must use their unique skills to uncover the reasons behind this inexplicable &quot;incident&quot;. Your choices will lead the protagonists towards different endings as you unraveling the underlying truth. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968970/extras/Timeline_2_eng_scaled_hq.gif?t=1729223069\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- <strong>Rich Characters Depths with Unique Perspectives</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You'll play as the four main characters as they navigate the lonely island plus each protagonist's &quot;dream scene&quot;, interact with over 20 vibrant characters, and solve various challenging problems. Each protagonist has their own unique way of engaging with their surroundings and others, as well as distinct styles in conversation and thinking. When faced with difficulties, switching between different character perspectives may lead to unexpected breakthroughs.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968970/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729223069","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968970/page.